Class ReflectionDBObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mongodb.ReflectionDBObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DBObject, BSONObject

    public abstract class ReflectionDBObject
extends Object
implements DBObject
    This class enables to map simple Class fields to a BSON object fields
